com.movo.wave

Enum WaveRequest.MarshalByte

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<WaveRequest.MarshalByte>
      • com.movo.wave.WaveRequest.MarshalByte
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<WaveRequest.MarshalByte>
    Enclosing class:
    WaveRequest

    public static enum WaveRequest.MarshalByte
extends java.lang.Enum<WaveRequest.MarshalByte>
    Enum for marshalling byte fields for byte array message exchanges with wave devices. Auto-detects sign conversion based on range. index: raw index in message byte array. min: lower (inclusive) bounds for byte value. max: upper (inclusive) bounds for byte value. offset: int offset to apply to byte value (additive on parse, subtractive on put).
